I feel like the people who gave these bad reviews probably didn't make them properly. Macaroons are sort of tricky because you have to do everything just right so that they look right and have the right texture. If you've never made macaroons like this before, I recommend watching this: http:// www.youtube.com/watch?v=qS4DJgFmNFM because it shows you how to make them very well. For the filling, I added vanilla extract into about half a bag of semisweet chocolate chips and about 1/4 cup of half and half for the filling, simply melting everything in the microwave because that's easier and faster. If I make them again, I might try using a white chocolate filling instead.

